Ask HN: How do you conduct your standup meetings?
text:
1) Do you go and just give your daily update?

2) Is it sync or async?

If sync:

4) When you are done, does the person who just provided an update select the next person who gives their update?

5) Is there some predetermined order?

6) Is there a designated leader who selects who goes next?
